N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1271.12 - Permission for jet-assisted take-offs required

State Regulations

Jet-assisted take-offs shall not be made at the air
terminal without obtaining the manager's permission and notifying the control
tower in advance. Notes
